#Class 5 Data Visualization

#Base R plot
plot(1:5)


#for prettier plots, we will use ggplot2 (already installed)
#install.packages("ggplot2")
library(ggplot2)

plot(cars)

p <- ggplot(cars) +
  aes(speed,dist) + 
  geom_point()

p + geom_line()

p + geom_smooth(method="lm")
## `geom_smooth()` using formula 'y ~ x'
